import React from "react";

const NavItem = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      className="ea-icon"

      viewBox="0 0 100 100"
    >
      <defs>
        <filter id="nav-blur" colorInterpolationFilters="sRGB">
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2.3" result="blur" />
          <feComposite
            in="SourceGraphic"
            in2="blur"
            operator="atop"
            result="composite1"
          />
          <feComposite in2="composite1" operator="in" result="composite2" />
          <feComposite in2="composite2" operator="in" result="composite3" />
        </filter>
      </defs>
      <path
      className="ea-base"
        d="M80.956 93.062l-28.009.79-28.005.029-8.515-26.528-9.748-25.56 22.776-17.329L51.672 7.633l22.534 16.116L96.94 39.034l-7.41 26.919z"
        fill="currentColor"
      />
      <path
        d="M62.706 268.425c-.427.308-11.124-13.153-11.652-13.155-.527-.002-11.316 13.386-11.742 13.075-.425-.312 9.072-14.645 8.91-15.147-.16-.502-16.227-6.626-16.062-7.127.164-.5 16.73 4.102 17.158 3.793.428-.308 1.288-17.48 1.815-17.479.527.002 1.269 17.18 1.694 17.492.426.31 17.024-4.178 17.185-3.676.16.502-15.947 6.516-16.112 7.017-.164.5 9.234 14.899 8.806 15.207z"
        transform="matrix(1.91195 0 0 1.8793 -44.408 -419.591)"
        className="ea-shine"
        fill="white"
        filter="url(#nav-blur)"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default NavItem;
